43
00:03:40,853 --> 00:03:43,754
Oh, I don't know.
It just seems...

44
00:03:43,823 --> 00:03:46,291
- it seems too fast.
- We're 36.

45
00:03:46,359 --> 00:03:48,827
I know,
but we're not 36, 36.

46
00:03:48,895 --> 00:03:50,920
Ahem...

47
00:03:50,997 --> 00:03:53,522
How much would you
sell them for?

48
