for us anyway.

52
00:04:10,383 --> 00:04:11,748
Okay.

53
00:04:14,020 --> 00:04:16,614
Remember that guy?
He made these little tables

54
00:04:16,689 --> 00:04:18,486
- out of string.
- Yes, I remember him.

55
00:04:18,558 --> 00:04:19,889
