56
00:04:21,594 --> 00:04:22,993
Bitch!

57
00:04:23,062 --> 00:04:25,690
Excuse me?

58
00:04:25,765 --> 00:04:27,665
Nothing.

59
00:04:33,539 --> 00:04:35,598
