61
00:04:36,943 --> 00:04:39,002
- It was great seeing you.
- You too.

62
00:04:39,078 --> 00:04:41,103
- You were always so creative.
- Yeah.

63
00:04:41,180 --> 00:04:44,741
No, it was...
I just ran into someone...

64
