Annie? Hey!

66
00:04:53,559 --> 00:04:56,522
How are you doing?

67
00:04:56,596 --> 00:04:59,064
Are you ready
for our first date?

68
00:04:59,132 --> 00:05:00,793
Pick you up later.

69
00:05:00,867 --> 00:05:03,062
I want
