72
00:05:10,009 --> 00:05:11,306
and reach out for me,
okay?

73
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:16,474
Good!
Reach out for me...

74
00:05:16,549 --> 00:05:20,144
Yes!
Good, see?

75
00:05:20,219 --> 00:05:22,619
How's you get
your hair to do that?

76
